Package: transportsimplex
Title: Transport composition data using Gaussian optimal transport
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Fernandes Machado, Agathe and Charpentier, Arthur and Gallic, Ewen
Maintainer: Agathe Fernandes Machado <fernandes_machado.agathe@courrier.uqam.ca>
Description: This package aims at creating counterfactuals for categorical 
  attributes of individuals from two different groups, using the representation
  of the attribute in the simplex (probability of belonging to each category)
  and relying on optimal transport to map characteristics from one group to the
  other.
